data.description: Situated in the tranquil Salado community, 4202 Big Brook offers an unparalleled living experience that exudes both modern luxury and rustic charm. Boasting almost an acre of private land, this 4-bedroom residence serves as a haven for those seeking both space and style. As you step through the front door, you'll immediately notice the home's meticulously designed interiors. Quartz countertops bring a touch of sophistication to the kitchen, while a beautiful fireplace in the living room serves as the heart of the home, ideal for cozy gatherings or quiet nights in. One of the standout features of this property is the spacious 800-square-foot structure.   Whether you envision it as a workshop, a home gym, or extra storage, the possibilities are endless. Come experience the comfort, elegance, and functionality that 4202 Big Brook has to offer. This is not just a place to live; it's a place to thrive!
